Comment: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:18.86,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.59,0:00:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人注意！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在開始我將對特洛斯特區奪還作戰進行說明
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要從向大家介紹這位士兵開始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.06,0:00:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫·耶格爾訓練兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.79,0:00:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我們秘密研製的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.58,0:00:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人化活體試驗中的成功案例
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.17,0:00:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變身為巨人的他將會舉起前門附近那塊巨石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把它搬運至被破壞的大門處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後堵住破洞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位的任務是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.50,0:00:36.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他搬運岩石的這段時間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:39.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護他免受別的巨人傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當此次作戰成功之時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.90,0:00:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類將第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.83,0:00:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功地從巨人手中奪回自己的領土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:53.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這和人類至今為止被奪去的東西相比
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定只是一次微不足道的小小勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.86,0:00:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一小步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於人類來說卻是進擊的一大步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫  你不認識我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是三笠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快閃開  阿克曼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:32.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是個腦子很笨的普通巨人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰計劃有變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回收耶格爾之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要保護他不受巨人傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他對人類來說是貴重的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.63,0:01:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能輕易放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.00,0:01:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來我在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.63,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓  為什麼不用立體機動裝置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裝置發生故障了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.88,0:02:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會想辦法解決的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰情況怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為不能扔下艾倫不管
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:20.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人越來越多  會全軍覆沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.90,0:02:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從後腦到頸部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.35,0:02:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,長1米  寬10釐米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:34.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫  回答我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要踏出牆外一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡就是地獄般的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還想前往外面的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你問我為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我生在了這個世界上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:45.01,PS,NTP,0,0,0,,原始的慾望\N{\fs-2}—特洛斯特區攻防戰{\fs-1}⑨—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳  我怎麼能拖他們後腿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能…有救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班長  到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.11,0:05:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只剩下我們兩個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時先退到岩石那邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有五隻巨人  從大門方向過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會一直等到巨人都走光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是機動裝置…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑  偏偏在這種時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓  冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.71,0:06:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬可
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.96,0:06:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  別給我們添麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳  為什麼扳機這麼硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這話應該是我問你吧  快點跳走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們都太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亂來的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.48,0:07:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不相信自己還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫他戰勝了自己的意識
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.70,0:08:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他現在正在努力完成自己的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後只要掩護艾倫至大門處
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:33.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們就贏了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我死守！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使要用我們的命來交換
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要保護艾倫到大門處！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:49.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能讓巨人接近他！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.47,0:08:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻礙他們的行動  掩護艾倫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩個人給我去艾倫的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是命令！明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米塔比班…  你們在做什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨人們根本不理我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們只有盡量接近來吸引它們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看這邊啊  混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不轉過來的話我就把刀插進你們的屁股裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了  有兩隻上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.14,0:09:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑起來  快往建築物那邊跑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會  降落到地面上無異於自殺行為啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有馬和建築物就沒法戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.60,0:09:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  現在只有這種方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟緊米塔比班！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿明  我們也快行動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.95,0:09:56.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過來  到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彷彿要四分五裂一般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.13,0:10:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三笠  阿明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種地方走來走去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:20.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會成為巨人的餌食的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.44,0:10:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快點過來啊  你這個傻大個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.72,0:10:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米塔比！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.97,0:10:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾倫為什麼還想前往外面的世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們所有人從出生的那一刻開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.59,0:10:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:11:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管有多麼強大的敵人來阻礙我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.38,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燃燒的水也好  冰凍的大地也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.97,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠看到那些的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:13.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是這個世界上最自由的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.27,0:11:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了自由我將不惜生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.25,0:11:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管世界多麼可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管世界多麼殘酷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有關係！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:51.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:56.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擋著路！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧  艾倫！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.36,0:12:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:53.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家的犧牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有白費啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.12,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰勝了巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.87,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認到了黃色煙霧彈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.15,0:13:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰好像成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.91,0:13:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊派遣援軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出精銳班
